verses.text_plain: I will extol thee, my God, O king; and I will bless thy name for ever and ever.
verses.verse_html: 1I will extol thee, my God, O king; and I will bless thy name for ever and ever.

verses.text_plain: Every day will I bless thee; and I will praise thy name for ever and ever.
verses.verse_html: 2Every day will I bless thee; and I will praise thy name for ever and ever.

verses.text_plain: Great is the Lord, and greatly to be praised; and his greatness is unsearchable.
verses.verse_html:
3Great is the Lord, and greatly to be praised; and his greatness is unsearchable. ▼
▼ and his…: Heb. and of his greatness there is no search

footnotes.body_text: ▼ and his…: Heb. and of his greatness there is no search
footnotes.body_html: ▼ and his…: Heb. and of his greatness there is no search

verses.text_plain: One generation shall praise thy works to another, and shall declare thy mighty acts.
verses.verse_html: 4One generation shall praise thy works to another, and shall declare thy mighty acts.

verses.text_plain: I will speak of the glorious honour of thy majesty, and of thy wondrous works.
verses.verse_html:
5I will speak of the glorious honour of thy majesty, and of thy wondrous works. ▼
▼ works: Heb. things, or, words

footnotes.body_html: ▼ works: Heb. things, or, words

verses.text_plain: And men shall speak of the might of thy terrible acts: and I will declare thy greatness.
verses.verse_html:
6And men shall speak of the might of thy terrible acts: and I will declare thy greatness. ▼
▼ declare: Heb. declare it

footnotes.body_html: ▼ declare: Heb. declare it

verses.text_plain: They shall abundantly utter the memory of thy great goodness, and shall sing of thy righteousness.
verses.verse_html: 7They shall abundantly utter the memory of thy great goodness, and shall sing of thy righteousness.

verses.text_plain: The Lord is gracious, and full of compassion; slow to anger, and of great mercy.
verses.verse_html:
8The Lord is gracious, and full of compassion; slow to anger, and of great mercy. ▼
▼ of great…: Heb. great in mercy

footnotes.body_text: ▼ of great…: Heb. great in mercy
footnotes.body_html: ▼ of great…: Heb. great in mercy

verses.text_plain: The Lord is good to all: and his tender mercies are over all his works.
verses.verse_html: 9The Lord is good to all: and his tender mercies are over all his works.

tokens.text: to all: and his tender mercies

verses.text_plain: All thy works shall praise thee, O Lord; and thy saints shall bless thee.
verses.verse_html: 10All thy works shall praise thee, O Lord; and thy saints shall bless thee.

verses.text_plain: They shall speak of the glory of thy kingdom, and talk of thy power;
verses.verse_html: 11They shall speak of the glory of thy kingdom, and talk of thy power;

verses.text_plain: To make known to the sons of men his mighty acts, and the glorious majesty of his kingdom.
verses.verse_html: 12To make known to the sons of men his mighty acts, and the glorious majesty of his kingdom.

verses.text_plain: Thy kingdom is an everlasting kingdom, and thy dominion endureth throughout all generations.
verses.verse_html:
13Thy kingdom is an everlasting kingdom, and thy dominion endureth throughout all generations. ▼
▼ an…: Heb. a kingdom of all ages

footnotes.body_text: ▼ an…: Heb. a kingdom of all ages
footnotes.body_html: ▼ an…: Heb. a kingdom of all ages

verses.text_plain: The Lord upholdeth all that fall, and raiseth up all those that be bowed down.
verses.verse_html: 14The Lord upholdeth all that fall, and raiseth up all those that be bowed down.

verses.text_plain: The eyes of all wait upon thee; and thou givest them their meat in due season.
verses.verse_html:
15The eyes of all wait upon thee; and thou givest them their meat in due season. ▼
▼ wait…: or, look unto

footnotes.body_html: ▼ wait…: or, look unto

verses.text_plain: Thou openest thine hand, and satisfiest the desire of every living thing.
verses.verse_html: 16Thou openest thine hand, and satisfiest the desire of every living thing.

verses.text_plain: The Lord is righteous in all his ways, and holy in all his works.
verses.verse_html:
17The Lord is righteous in all his ways, and holy in all his works. ▼
▼ holy: or, merciful, or, bountiful

footnotes.body_html: ▼ holy: or, merciful, or, bountiful

verses.text_plain: The Lord is nigh unto all them that call upon him, to all that call upon him in truth.
verses.verse_html: 18The Lord is nigh unto all them that call upon him, to all that call upon him in truth.

tokens.text: upon him, to all that call

verses.text_plain: He will fulfil the desire of them that fear him: he also will hear their cry, and will save them.
verses.verse_html: 19He will fulfil the desire of them that fear him: he also will hear their cry, and will save them.

verses.text_plain: The Lord preserveth all them that love him: but all the wicked will he destroy.
verses.verse_html: 20The Lord preserveth all them that love him: but all the wicked will he destroy.

verses.text_plain: My mouth shall speak the praise of the Lord: and let all flesh bless his holy name for ever and ever.
verses.verse_html: 21My mouth shall speak the praise of the Lord: and let all flesh bless his holy name for ever and ever.
